<para>
  The <classname>SegmentChooser</classname> objects are used to define
  a set of &skel; &sgmts; which will be considered as potential
  subdivision targets.  They're used when the
  <varname>targets</varname> parameter of the <xref
  linkend="RegisteredClass-Refine"/> &skel; modifier is set to <xref
  linkend="RegisteredClass-CheckHeterogeneousSegments"/>.
</para>

